title: Looking for Silver-gold Top Laner for Competitive Team
body:
We are looking for silver-gold top laner for a competitive team. We will play in tournaments and practice in ranked flex often. If you are interested in joining here is a link to the sign up form.

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1uyc2TTvRraY33RCjfyKX-v_qgNhsmQBc63z1SHXaJiA/edit
